&lt;li&gt;Build and own executive dashboards and reporting cadences that provide actionable insight to the CEO, CFO, and leadership team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with Finance, Data, and Operations to ensure data integrity, consistency, and accessibility across KPI reporting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive quarterly and annual OKR/goal-setting processes, tracking progress and flagging risks to plan.&lt;/li&gt;
