&lt;li&gt;Triage and troubleshoot infrastructure issues and outages in real time, and drive root cause analysis to prevent recurrence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handle security-related tickets, such as fixing and maintaining GitHub Actions and keeping client/dependency versions up to date&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement and enforce security and compliance best practices, including access control, certificate management, vulnerability management, and audit logging&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluate and roll out new infrastructure and tooling, advising Engineering, Product, and Design on the best way to adopt and integrate them&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Data Engineering to support data infrastructure and pipeline needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage vendor relationships for networking hardware, cloud services, and security tooling; guiding the organization in strategic build vs. buy decisions to maximize ROI&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive infrastructure-as-code adoption to ensure reproducible, auditable environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Product and Leadership to translate operational needs into scalable infrastructure solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay current on AI infrastructure trends and help evaluate their application to Ghost’s platform&lt;/li&gt;
